%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tanker%20Hit%20off%20Gujarat%20Coast%20by%20Drone%20Fired%20From%20Iran%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F17123254%2Fcontainer-ship-560789_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20According%20to%20the%20US%20military%2C%20a%20drone%20fired%20from%20Iran%20has%20hit%20a%20Japanese-owned%20chemical%20tanker%20located%20around%20370%20kilometres%20from%20the%20Indian%20coast%20off%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBBC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67811929%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20December%2024.%20Though%20the%20hit%20caused%20structural%20damage%2C%20no%20casualties%20have%20been%20reported%20and%20a%20fire%20aboard%20the%20tanker%20was%20put%20out.%20The%20Indian%20navy%20has%20sent%20an%20aircraft%20and%20warships%20for%20assistance%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BBC%20reported%20that%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20said%20that%20the%20tanker%20%E2%80%93%20named%20%E2%80%9CChem%20Pluto%E2%80%9D%2C%20donning%20a%20Liberian%20flag%20and%20operated%20by%20the%20Netherlands%20%E2%80%93%20was%20hit%20by%20%E2%80%9Ca%20one-way%20attack%20drone%20fired%20from%20Iran%E2%80%9D.%20The%20AFP%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voanews.com%2Fa%2Ftanker-ship-off-india-hit-by-attack-drone-fired-from-iran-pentagon-says-%2F7410477.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20per%20the%20statement%2C%20the%20US%20military%20is%20in%20communication%20with%20the%20vessel%20%E2%80%9Cas%20it%20continues%20toward%20a%20destination%20in%20India%E2%80%9D%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20on%20December%2023%20(06%3A00%20GMT)%2C%20per%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ukmto.org%2Findian-ocean%2Frecent-incidents%23%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUnited%20Kingdom%20Maritime%20Trade%20Operations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(UKMTO)%2C%20which%20provides%20information%20on%20maritime%20security%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20and%20the%20Arabian%20Sea.%20The%20UKMTO%20reported%20that%20it%20received%20news%20of%20an%20attack%20%E2%80%9Capproximately%20200%20NM%20%5Bnautical%20miles%5D%20South%20West%20of%20Veraval%2C%20India%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cauthorities%20are%20investigating%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20attack%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20drone%20and%20missile%20strikes%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67614911%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHouthi%20rebels%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20an%20Iran-backed%20group%20which%20controls%20a%20large%20part%20of%20Yemen%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20on%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20which%20is%20an%20important%20shipping%20route.%20According%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67614911%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBBC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20attacks%20began%20after%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20with%20the%20Houthis%20declaring%20their%20support%20for%20Hamas.%20Their%20means%20of%20showing%20this%20support%20has%20been%20by%20attacking%20cargo%20and%20commercial%20vessels%20bound%20for%2C%20or%20linked%20to%2C%20Israel.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20many%20shipping%20companies%20have%20stopped%20going%20via%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20choosing%20to%20reroute%20their%20vessels%20south%20of%20Africa%20despite%20the%20longer%20route%20and%20higher%20fuel%20costs.%20The%20US%2C%20along%20with%20more%20than%2020%20countries%2C%20has%20set%20up%20a%20multinational%20naval%20task%20force%20to%20protect%20ship%20movements%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voanews.com%2Fa%2Ftanker-ship-off-india-hit-by-attack-drone-fired-from-iran-pentagon-says-%2F7410477.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAFP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20US%20has%20openly%20accused%20Iran%2C%20which%20is%20known%20to%20support%20Hamas%2C%20of%20directly%20targeting%20ships%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%20Per%20the%20BBC%2C%20Iran%20has%20not%20commented%20on%20the%20drone%20attack%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20vessel%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0yet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20Israel%20had%20alleged%20that%20Yemen%E2%80%99s%20Houthi%20rebels%20were%20responsible%20for%20the%20hijacking%20of%20an%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-alleges-houthi-rebel-hand-behind-hijacking-of-india-bound-cargo-ship-in-red-sea%5C%22%3E%20Israeli-linked%20cargo%20ship%20headed%20from%20Turkey%20to%20India%20via%20the%20Red%20Sea%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20hijacked%20vessel%20had%20been%20in%20Korfez%2C%20Turkey%2C%20and%20was%20on%20its%20way%20to%20Pipavav%2C%20India%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20seizure%20reported%20by%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703422437000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ftanker-hit-off-gujarat-coast-by-drone-fired-from-iran-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20attack%20caused%20damages%20to%20the%20Japanese-owned%20ship%2C%20no%20casualties%20have%20been%20reported%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%20appears%20to%20show%20'exceptional%20levels%20of%20rat%20and%20mic