0charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657739df7a3c8094d5db9f30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222094%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20reporter%20at%20a%20restaurant%20in%20Manhattan.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Parker%20Erb%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI've%20done%C2%A0%26quot%3BDry%20January%26quot%3B%20every%20year%20since%202019.%20Next%20month%20will%20mark%20my%20sixth%20year%20doing%20the%20trend.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20me%2C%20it%20was%20a%20way%20to%20become%20healthier%20and%20more%20productive%20during%20the%20new%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20my%20first%20time%2C%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20it.%20I%20feel%20like%20it%20sets%20the%20tone%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20final%20semester%20of%20college%20in%202019%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20were%20getting%20serious%20with%20my%20classes%2C%20work%2C%20and%20final%20projects%2C%20and%20I%20needed%20to%20kick%20it%20into%20high%20gear%20to%20push%20through%20the%20last%20few%20months%20before%20graduation.%20Though%20the%20concept%20of%20%26quot%3BDry%20January%26quot%3B%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Falcoholchange.org.uk%2Fhelp-and-support%2Fmanaging-your-drinking%2Fdry-january%2Fabout-dry-january%2Fthe-dry-january-story%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoined%20in%202013%20by%20a%20charity%20in%20the%20UK%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I'd%20only%20heard%20of%20it%20in%20late%202018%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20by%20the%20first%20day%20of%202019%2C%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20give%20it%20a%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20is%20simple%20(give%20up%20alcohol%20for%20the%20month%20of%20January)%20and%20the%20benefits%20are%20many%20(no%20hangovers%2C%20get%20healthier%2C%20save%20money).%20Forgoing%20drinking%20can%20be%20a%20challenge%2C%20but%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20I've%20found%20a%20few%20ways%20to%20make%20it%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20share%20my%20plans%20with%20the%20people%20close%20to%20me.%20It%20helps%20keep%20me%20accountable.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20I%20tell%20my%20friends%20and%20family%20about%20my%20intention%20to%20do%20Dry%20January.%20I'm%20lucky%20to%20be%20surrounded%20by%20supportive%20people%20who%2C%20although%20they%20may%20want%20me%20to%20go%20out%20for%20a%20night%20on%20the%20town%2C%20accept%20my%20choices%20and%20don't%20pressure%20me%20into%20drinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.health.harvard.edu%2Fblog%2Fthinking-of-trying-dry-january-steps-for-success-202201032662%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarvard%20Men's%20Health%20Watch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20publication%20from%20the%20medical%20school%2C%20suggests%20telling%20your%20social%20circle%20and%20%26quot%3Bencouraging%20them%20to%20keep%20you%20accountable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaying%20your%20intentions%20out%20loud%2C%20to%20your%20people%2C%20is%20a%20simple%20way%20to%20stay%20on%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESometimes%2C%20I%20can%20get%20a%20buddy%20to%20try%20Dry%20January%20with%20me%2C%20and%20we%20can%20help%20each%20other%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Friends%20at%20bar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dafe441f51cc0019698b8b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BDry%20January%26quot%3B%20can%20be%20easier%20if%20you%20have%20a%20friend%20to%20experience%20it%20with.%3Cp%3EGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20it%20when%20a%20friend%20joins%20me%20on%20a%20Dry%20January%20journey.%20It's%20fun%20to%20find%20things%20to%20do%20together%20that%20don't%20involve%20drinking%2C%20and%20frankly%2C%20it's%20just%20nice%20to%20have%20someone%20going%20through%20the%20same%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20admit%20that%20giving%20up%20alcohol%20can%20be%20a%20challenge%2C%20especially%20when%20it's%20become%20so%20integrated%20into%20social%20life.%20But%20having%20another%20person%20trying%20out%20the%20same%20thing%20makes%20it%20feel%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20lean%20into%20the%20hobbies%20that%20bring%20me%20the%20most%20happiness%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20lot%20easier%20to%20get%20to%20the%20gym%20or%20a%20workout%20class%20when%20you're%20not%20hungover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHitting%20the%20gym%20is%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20pastimes%2C%20and%20it%20becomes%20so%20much%20easier%20when%20I%20can%20spring%20out%20of%20bed%2C%20rested%20and%20hydrated%20without%20a%20night%20of%20drinking%20behind%20me.%20Every%20January%20I%20get%20deeper%20into%20my%20fitness%20journey%2C%20setting%20myself%20up%20with%20a%20healthy%20habit%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20give%20up%20drinking%2C%20I%20also%20have%20more%20free%20time%20in%20the%20evenings%20to%20do%20other%20things%20I%20enjoy%2C%20like%20reading%20or%20cozying%20up%20on%20the%20couch%20to%20watch%20bad%20reality%20television.%20It%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20say%20no%20to%20a%20night%20out%2C%20but%20I%20use%20it%20as%20a%20way%20to%20reconnect%20with%20the%20things%20I%20like%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-do-dry-january-sobriety-tips-advice-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703421841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65773a0c0ec98e92f74e1e70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-do-dry-january-sobriety-tips-advice-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDry%20January%2C%26quot%3B%20wherein%20practitioners%20cut%20out%20alcohol%20for%20the%20first%20month%20of%20the%20year%2C%20has%20boomed%20in%20popularity%20recently.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jerb%40businessinsider.com%20(Jordan%20Parker%20Erb)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22ht