0Bali.%20I%20paid%20%247%2C000%20in%20school%20fees%2C%20and%20classes%20began%20in%20June%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20a%20long-term%20rental%20at%20Pererenan%2C%20Canggu%2C%20a%20seaside%20village%20near%20the%20boot%20camp%20premises.%20I%20stayed%20in%20a%20one-bedroom%20rental%20in%20a%20shared%20villa%20with%20another%20guest%20and%20a%20live-in%20landlord.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nine-week%20boot%20camp%20was%20really%20intensive.%20Classes%20took%20place%20only%20on%20the%20weekdays.%20They%20would%20start%20at%20about%209%20a.m.%20and%20would%20go%20on%20until%20about%206%20or%207%20p.m.%20Sometimes%2C%20the%20class%20would%20go%20out%20for%20dinner%20together%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20an%20unintended%20benefit%20to%20taking%20the%20course%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20There%20were%20only%20about%20eight%20students%20in%20my%20class.%20Ordinarily%2C%20there%20would've%20been%2020%20or%2030%20of%20them%20in%20a%20batch.%20That%20allowed%20our%20teachers%20to%20devote%20more%20attention%20to%20each%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20the%20environment%20there%20made%20it%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20on%20holiday.%20We%20had%20our%20classes%20on%20the%20top%20floor%20of%20a%20hotel%20facing%20the%20ocean!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jessica%20Kalip%20and%20her%20classmates%20from%20the%20coding%20boot%20camp.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6572d2cd0ec98e92f74d63e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKalip%20(second%20from%20left)%20and%20her%20classmates%20from%20the%20coding%20boot%20camp%20in%20Bali.%3Cp%3EJessica%20Kalip%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EJob%20hunting%20during%20the%20pandemic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20boot%20camp%20ended%2C%20I%20took%20some%20time%20to%20learn%20additional%20programming%20languages%20and%20frameworks.%20I%20also%20comp