d%20with%20him%2C%20but%20then%20I%20got%20into%20my%20teenage%20years%20and%20thought%20maybe%20I'd%20want%20to%20do%20my%20own%20thing.%20I%20thought%20about%20moving%20to%20Colorado%2C%20but%20when%20I%20really%20considered%20it%2C%20I%20changed%20my%20mind%20to%20Alaska.%20Lots%20of%20my%20friends%20were%20moving%20to%20Denver%20and%20I%20was%20excited%20about%20going%20to%20concerts%20at%20Red%20Rocks%2C%20but%20then%20I%20started%20to%20think%20I%20didn't%20really%20want%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20big%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223409%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Whittier%2C%20Alaska.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6585d2e01c5c7b8c9a0b9775%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221944%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhittier%2C%20Alaska%3Cp%3Eannhfhung%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20selling%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20stuff%20and%20fitting%20whatever%20was%20left%20over%20into%20my%20Subuaru.%20I%20drove%2014%20hours%20to%20Washington%20and%20then%20caught%20a%20ferry.%20I%20had%20never%20seen%20anything%20like%20that%20before.%20I%20didn't%20know%20they%20made%20boats%20that%20big.%20We%20traveled%20for%20four%20days%20across%20the%20ocean%20all%20the%20way%20to%20Whittier%2C%20Alaska.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHousing%20is%20cheap%20but%20McDonalds%20is%20expensive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20working%20at%20a%20car%20dealership%20back%20in%20Wyoming%20and%20didn't%20have%20anything%20lined%20up%20in%20Alaska.%20But%20there's%20so%20much%20opportunity%20up%20here.%20I%20walked%20into%20a%20dealership%20and%20just%20asked%20for%20a%20job%20and%20they%20gave%20it%20to%20me.%20Eventually%20I%20got%20my%20real-estate%20license%20and%20now%20I%20work%20as%20an%20agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20hard%20to%20find%20a%20place%20to%20live.%20I%20had%20maybe%20%243%2C000%20in%20savings%20and%20lived%20with%20my%20dad%20for%20six%20months%20to%20get%20adjusted.%20But%2C%20I%