%20Anything%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20secret%20is%20to%20go%20to%20Hawaii.%20You've%20got%20to%20take%20a%20vacation%20at%20least%20once%20during%20the%20winter%20up%20here.%20You%20can%20get%20tickets%20from%20Anchorage%20to%20Hawaii%20for%2C%20like%2C%20%24300.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Flint%20Selby%20holds%20a%203-foot%20fish%20he%20caught%20on%20an%20Alaskan%20fishing%20boat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6585e9941c5c7b8c9a0baa28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESelby%20considered%20Colorado%2C%20but%20felt%20Alaska%20offered%20even%20more%20wilderness%20experiences.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Flint%20Selby%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20in%20summer%20it's%20literally%20light%20for%2022%20hours.%20If%20you%20go%20to%20North%20Country%2C%20up%20to%20Fairbanks%2C%20it'll%20be%20light%20for%2024%20hours.%20You'll%20be%20sitting%20around%20a%20bonfire%20with%20your%20buddies%20and%20suddenly%20realize%20it's%204%20a.m.%20It%20feels%20like%20no%20time%20passes%2C%20it's%20incredible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20get%20the%20only-in-Alaska%20experiences%2C%20like%20waking%20up%20early%20morning%20to%20let%20your%20dog%20go%20outside%20and%20coming%20face%20to%20face%20with%20a%20moose.%20They're%20absolutely%20everywhere%20%E2%80%94%20I%20see%20them%20all%20the%20time.%20And%20sometimes%20the%20moose%20can%20be%20a%20little%20bit%20scary.%20They're%20huge.%20I'm%206'6%26quot%3B%20and%20they're%20taller%20than%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20just%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20you%20look%20a%20little%20bit%20big%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20look%20like%20you're%20trying%20to%20prey%20on%20them.%20I've%20had%20to%20pull%20my%20dog%20back%20because%20he'll%20start%20barking%20and%20that%20will%20get%20them%20upset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIt's%20been%20easy%20to%20acclimate%20to%20living%20here%20because%20of%20the%20people%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20have%20any%20friends%20at%20first%20and%20I%20was%20super%20worried%20about%20making%20friends.%20But%20there%20are%20just%20so%20many%20good%20people.%20Everyone%20is%20so%20inviting.%20You%20can%20walk%20through%20the%20store%20and%20start%20a%20conversation%20with%20someone.%20I've%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20friends%20through%20work%20and%20honestly%20just%20going%20to%20the%20bar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225049%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20moose%20stands%20in%20an%20Alaskan%20field%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6585eaa41c5c7b8c9a0baaf4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223366%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESelby%20wasn't%20prepared%20to%20come%20face-to-face%20with%20intimidating%20moose%3Cp%3EPatrick%20J.%20Endres%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20looking%20to%20move%20to%20Alaska%2C%20my%20tip%20is%20get%20a%20U-Haul.%20I%20sold%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20stuff%20but%20that%20made%20it%20harder%20to%20get%20settled.%20Get%20a%20U-Haul%20and%20make%20the%20drive%20through%20Canada.%20Get%20a%20really%20good%20jacket%20and%20boots.%20An%20Alaskan%20staple%20is%20Xtratuf%20boots%2C%20these%20rubber%20boots%20that%20are%20insulated.%20You'll%20see%20them%20everywhere%20up%20here%2C%20people%20walking%20around%20with%20brown%20and%20yellow%20boots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20I%20am%20so%20glad%20I%20live%20here.%20There's%20just%20so%20much%20to%20do.%20If%20you%20like%20getting%20outdoors%2C%20this%20is%20the%20place%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-in-alaska-pros-cons-outdoors-no-sunlight-cheap-rent-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703420642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6585ecc4cefc010bea26de51%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessi