ernments%20can%20even%20consider%20suppressing%20these%20protests%2C%20and%20sooner%20or%20later%2C%20these%20will%20have%20their%20effect%20on%20the%20policies%20of%20these%20countries.%20This%20is%20how%20genuine%20democracies%20give%20voice%20to%20their%20citizens%E2%80%99%20concerns%20against%20their%20own%20governments%20turning%20rogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20London%20Metropolitan%20police%20recently%20provided%20another%20example%20of%20how%20real%20democracies%20work.%20Various%20organisations%20had%20planned%20a%20massive%20march%20in%20support%20of%20Palestine%20on%20Armistice%20Day%20last%20month.%20British%20Home%20Secretary%20Suella%20Braverman%20and%20the%20government%20of%20Uncle%20Tom%20(brazenly%20pro-Israel)%20wanted%20the%20police%20to%20deny%20permission%20for%20it.%20The%20police%20commissioner%20refused%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20there%20was%20no%20threat%20to%20law%20and%20order%20and%20he%20could%20not%20legally%20ban%20the%20march.%20Braverman%20went%20public%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20accusing%20the%20London%20police%20of%20partisanship%20and%20selective%20favouritism.%20The%20commissioner%20stood%20his%20ground%2C%20the%20march%20went%20ahead%20peacefully%2C%20the%20only%20arrests%20were%20of%20some%20right%20wing%20elements%20who%20attempted%20to%20disrupt%20it.%20And%20guess%20what%3F%20There%20was%20so%20much%20anger%20and%20outrage%20against%20Braverman%20that%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20later%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20had%20to%20sack%20the%20her.%20This%20is%20how%20democracies%20work.%20Not%20like%20our%20own%20police%20who%20have%20become%20like%20private%20militias%20of%20any%20ruling%20party%2C%20whether%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20Union%20or%20state%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-last-pillar-of-indian-democracy-has-fallen%5C%22%3EThe%20Last%20Pillar%20of%20Indian%20Democracy%20Has%20Fallen%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20defence%20chiefs%20are%20looking%20increasingly%20like%20men%20of%20straw%2C%20not%20withstanding%20their%20impressively%20resplendent%20uniforms%2C%20with%20more%20stars%20than%20in%20the%20Milky%20Way.%20They%20have%20been%20silent%20even%20as%20the%20political%20executive%20has%20run%20rough%20shod%20over%20their%20decades%20old%20culture%20and%20ethos%2C%20changing%20their%20regimental%20traditions%2C%20ranks%2C%20uniforms%2C%20mode%20of%20recruitment%2C%20perhaps%20even%20interfering%20in%20operational%20and%20tactical%20matters.%20And%20now%2C%20we%20are%20told%2C%20some%20of%20these%20retired%20worthies%20may%20even%20be%20attending%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20a%20politico-religious%20event%2C%20further%20eroding%20the%20apolitical%20and%20religion-neutral%20ethos%20of%20our%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompare%20this%20with%20the%20stance%20adopted%20by%20General%20Milley%2C%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20US%20Joint%20Chiefs%20of%20Staff%2C%20who%20resisted%20every%20move%20by%20Trump%20to%20use%20the%20military%20to%20stay%20on%20in%20power.%20He%20made%20his%20reservations%20clear%20to%20the%20White%20House%20and%20almost%20resigned%20in%20June%202020%2C%20but%20then%20told%20his%20staff%3A%20%E2%80%9D%20If%20they%20want%20to%20court-martial%20me%20or%20put%20me%20in%20prison%2C%20have%20at%20it%E2%80%A6.I%20will%20fight%20from%20the%20inside.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReal%20democracies%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20fake%20ones.%20respect%20their%20citizens%E2%80%99%20sentiments%2C%20do%20not%20suppress%20them%20by%20the%20use%20of%20force%2C%20and%20have%20robust%20institutions%20and%20civil%20societies%20that%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted%20at%20critical%20moments.%20We%20are%20not%20yet%20a%20fake%20democracy%2C%20but%20we%20are%20getting%20there%20fast.%20Democracies%20do%20not%20die%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20governments%20alone%3A%20when%20public%20conscience%20and%20opinion%20dies%2C%20so%20do%