ohn's%20deceased%20son%2C%20Lee%2C%20in%20episode%20seven.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22John%20moves%20into%20Lee's%20(Dave%20Annable)%20cabin%20in%20episode%20seven%20of%20%26quot%3BYellowstone%26quot%3B%20season%20two.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657f92a01c5c7b8c9a092037%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222036%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn%20moves%20into%20Lee's%20(Dave%20Annable)%20cabin%20in%20episode%20seven%20of%20%26quot%3BYellowstone%26quot%3B%20season%20two.%3Cp%3EParamount%20Network%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20someone%20who%20was%20set%20to%20inherit%20the%20ranch%20and%20continue%20the%20Dutton%20legacy%2C%20John's%20eldest%20son%20Lee%20(Dave%20Annable)%20sure%20doesn't%20get%20mentioned%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20viewers%20will%20remember%2C%20he%20was%20shot%20and%20killed%20in%20a%20shootout%20in%20the%20show's%20pilot%20episode%2C%20which%20set%20in%20motion%20John's%20decision%20to%20bring%20his%20other%20three%20children%20back%20to%20the%20ranch%20and%20work%20out%20who%20is%20the%20right%20fit%20to%20take%20over%20his%20role%20when%20he%20dies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Lee%20is%20all%20but%20forgotten%20this%20season%2C%20there%20is%20a%20nod%20to%20him%20in%20episode%20seven%20after%20Kayce%20agrees%20to%20once%20again%20live%20at%20the%20ranch.%20To%20give%20Kayce%20and%20his%20family%20space%2C%20John%20decides%20to%20move%20into%20Lee's%20old%20cabin%20on%20the%20land%2C%20which%20leads%20to%20an%20emotional%20confrontation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20moving%20his%20personal%20belongings%20into%20the%20cabin%2C%20John%20can't%20help%20but%20feel%20like%20he's%20desecrating%20Lee's%20memory.%20It's%20clear%20the%20cabin%20hasn't%20been%20touched%20since%20Lee's%20death%2C%20and%20John%20even%20apologizes%20when%20he%20starts%20making%20changes%20to%20the%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20not%20mention%20