st-fall-fashion-looks-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estyling%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kate's%20public%20perception%20has%20shifted%20to%20being%20accepted%20by%20the%20public%20as%20a%20future%20queen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECelebrities%20downplaying%20their%20wealth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20all%20likely%20seen%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-spent-160-hours-using-private-jet-eras-tour-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheadlines%20about%20Swift's%20private%20jet%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-spent-160-hours-using-private-jet-eras-tour-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrips%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20her%20Eras%20tour%2C%20but%20that's%20where%20our%20knowledge%20of%20Swift's%20wealth%20ends.%20We%20don't%20see%20her%20driving%20sports%20cars%20or%20singing%20about%20her%20money%20or%20expensive%20possessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrchard%20said%20while%20some%20celebrities%20do%20downplay%20their%20wealth%2C%20it%20depends%20on%20who%20the%20celebrity%20is%20and%20what%20their%20audience%20cares%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20Kim%20Kardashian%20is%20an%20example%20of%20a%20celebrity%20who%20makes%20no%20attempt%20to%20hide%20their%20lavish%20lifestyle%2C%20be%20that%20with%20her%20purse%20collection%20or%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fkim-kardashian-hailey-bieber-mile-high-club-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprivate%20jet%20trips%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Orchard%20said%20this%20works%20for%20Kardashian's%20fan%20base%20as%20they%20like%20watching%20something%20aspirational%20and%20near%20impossible%20to%20attain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20fans%20say%20Swift's%20style%20leaves%20much%20to%20be%20desired%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20time%20when%20image%20is%20everything%2C%20there's%20a%20hunger%20for%20Swift%20to%20experiment%20with%20her%20style%20and%20fans%20have%20been%20vocal%20on