ssinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-quiet-luxury-style-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20Asks%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20To%20Form%20Panel%20To%20Run%20Wrestling%20Body%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Sports%20Ministry%20has%20asked%20the%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20(IOA)%20to%20form%20a%20temporary%20panel%20to%20run%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%2C%20whose%20newly%20elected%20management%20has%20been%20suspended%20amid%20a%20row%20with%20wrestlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20IOA%20chief%2C%20the%20Sports%20Ministry%20said%20the%20temporary%20committee%20can%20manage%20and%20control%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20WFI%20including%20selection%20of%20athletes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20Taking%20note%20of%20the%20compelling%20current%20situation%20arising%20out%20of%20the%20influence%20and%20control%20of%20the%20WFI's%20former%20office%20bearers%2C%20serious%20concerns%20have%20arisen%20about%20the%20governance%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20WFI%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20letter%20signed%20by%20Tarun%20Pareek%2C%20undersecretary%20to%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20requires%20for%20immediate%20and%20stringent%20corrective%20measures%20to%20uphold%20the%20principles%20of%20good%20governance%20in%20sports%20organisations%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20now%20it%20becomes%20incumbent%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20IOA%20to%20make%20suitable%20arrangements%20for%20the%20interim%20period%20for%20managing%20the%20affairs%20of%20WFI%2C%20so%20that%20sportspersons%20of%20wrestling%20discipline%20do%20not%20suffer%20in%20any%20manner%20and%20the%20principle%20of%20good%20governance%20is%20the%20sports%20body%20do%20not%20get%20jeopardised%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Sports%20Ministry%20said%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20round%20of%20election%20to%20the%20WFI%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out%20since%20the%20latest%20administration%20led%20by%20the%20newly%20elected%20chief%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20a%20loyalist%20of%20former%20WFI%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20has%20been%20suspended%20by%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20temporary%20panel%20formed%20by%20the%20IOA%20will%20look%20after%20the%20day-to-day%20affairs%20of%20the%20WFI%2C%20including%20making%20entries%20for%20participation%20of%20sportspersons%20in%20international%20events%2C%20and%20holding%20sporting%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAce%20wrestler%20Sakshee%20Malikkh%20had%20raised%20concerns%20yesterday%20regarding%20the%20upcoming%20junior%20national%20competitions%2C%20following%20with%20the%20Centre%20ordered%20the%20newly-elected%20WFI%20panel%20to%20stop%20all%20activities%20till%20further%20orders.%20The%20Centre%20also%20noted%20the%20%26quot%3Bhasty%26quot%3B%20announcement%20of%20the%20junior%20national%20contests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sports%20Ministry%20in%20a%20statement%20noted%20the%20newly%20elected%20body%20%26quot%3Bappears%20to%20be%20(in)%20complete%20control%20of%20former%20office%20bearers%20in%20complete%20disregard%20to%20the%20Sports%20Code%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20business%20of%20WFI%2C%20the%20ministry%20said%2C%20is%20being%20run%20from%20the%20premises%20controlled%20by%20former%20office%20bearers.%20%26quot%3BWhich%20is%20also%20alleged%20premises%20wherein%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20the%20players%20have%20been%20alleged%20and%20(at)%20present%20the%20court%20in%20hearing%20the%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrij%20Bhushan%2C%20a%20six-time%20BJP%20MP%2C%20had%20to%20step%20aside%20after%20the%20country's%20top%20wrestlers%2C%20including%20Ms%20Malikkh%2C%20accused%20him%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20women%20wrestlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20wrestlers%2C%20also%20including%20Olympic%20bronze%20medallist%20Bajrang%20Punia%20and%20Commonwealth%20Games%20gold%20medallist%20Vinesh%20Phogat%2C%20hit%20the%20streets%20in%20January%20to%20seek%20action%20against%20the%20BJP%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20called%20off%20the%20agitation%20following%20assurances%20from%20the%20government.%20A%20probe%20was%20also%20launched%20against%20Brij%20Bhushan.%20The%20recent%20WFI%20election%20saw%20Sanjay%20Singh%20post%20a%20thumping%20victory%20against%20Commonwealth%20Games%20gold%20medallist%20Anita%20Sheoran%2C%20who%20was%20backed%20by%20the%20protesting%20wrestlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20assurances%20that%20close%20aides%20and%20relatives%20of%20Brij%20Bhushan%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20contest%20the%20polls%2C%20the%20nomination%20of%20Sanjay%20Singh%20was%20cleared.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703417880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Fa90k1l6o_wrestlers-protest_625x300_20_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-asks-indian-olympic-association-to-form-panel-to-run-wrestling-body-4734020%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Sports%20Ministry%20has%20asked%20the%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20(IOA)%20to%20form%20a%20temporary%20panel%20to%20run%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%2C%20whose%20newly%20elected%20management%20has%20been%20suspended%20amid%20a%20row%20with%20wrestlers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-asks-indian-olympic-association-to-form-panel-to-run-wrestling-body-4734020%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-asks-indian-olympic-association-to-form-panel-to-run-wrestling-body-4734020%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-asks-indian-olympic-association-to-form-panel-to-run-wrestling-body-4734020%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%202%20Men%20On%20Horse%20Try%20To%20Steal%20Temple%20Donation%20Box%2C%20What%20Happened%20Next%22%2C%22content%22%3A