ds%20days%20before%20Christmas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703416920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F768x432%2Fskynews-cctv-australia-meat_6403205.jpg%3F20231224112711%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fthieves-steal-seafood-and-meat-worth-thousands-from-australian-butcher-days-before-christmas-13037315%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20thieves%20have%20raided%20thousands%20of%20pounds%20worth%20of%20seafood%20and%20meat%20from%20a%20butchers%20in%20South%20Australia%20last%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fthieves-steal-seafood-and-meat-worth-thousands-from-australian-butcher-days-before-christmas-13037315%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20MP's%20'Bhumihar-Rajput'%20Reply%20To%20Question%20On%20New%20Wrestling%20Boss%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20huge%20row%20surrounding%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20today%20said%20he%20will%20never%20contest%20the%20wrestling%20body's%20polls%20again%20and%20distanced%20himself%20from%20new%20WFI%20president%20Sanjay%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six-time%20BJP%20MP%2C%20who%20led%20the%20wrestling%20body%20for%2012%20years%2C%20had%20to%20step%20aside%20earlier%20this%20year%20after%20the%20country's%20top%20wrestlers%20took%20to%20the%20streets%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20women%20wrestlers.%20In%20the%20recently-held%20WFI%20polls%2C%20his%20aide%20Sanjay%20Singh%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20top%20post.%20Sanjay%20Singh%20has%20said%20he%20is%20close%20to%20the%20BJP%20MP%2C%20but%20denied%20that%20he%20was%20a%20dummy%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20mediaperson's%20question%20on%20whether%20Sanjay%20Singh%20was%20close%20to%20him%2C%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSanjay%20Singh%20is%20a%20Bhumihar.%20I%20am%20Rajput%2C%20Kshatriya.%20There%20can%20be%20a%20relationship%2C%20friendship.%20He%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20wrestling%20for%2015%20years.%20Is%20there%20anyone%20in%20the%20wrestling%20circle%20who%20does%20not%20have%20acquaintance%20with%20me%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20MP%20was%20also%20asked%20about%20his%20%26quot%3Bdabdaba%26quot%3B%20remark%20after%20the%20WFI%20poll%20results%2C%20in%20which%20he%20had%20implied%20that%20his%20dominance%20on%20the%20federation%20will%20continue.%20Today%2C%20he%20just%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BJo%20aayi%20woh%20gayi%26quot%3B%20-%20meaning%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20came%20has%20left%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20heavyweight%20spoke%20to%20the%20media%20shortly%20after%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Youth%20Affairs%20and%20Sports%20rapped%20the%20newly-formed%20WFI%20panel%20for%20its%20hasty%20announcement%20of%20junior%20national%20wrestling%20contests.%20The%20ministry%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20newly%20elected%20body%20%26quot%3Bappears%20to%20be%20(in)%20complete%20control%20of%20former%20office%20bearers%20in%20complete%20disregard%20to%20the%20Sports%20Code%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry's%20action%20came%20after%20Olympic%20bronze%20medallist%20Sakshee%20Malikkh's%2C%20whose%20decision%20to%20quit%20wrestling%20after%20Sanjay%20Singh's%20election%20had%20sparked%20outrage%2C%20put%20up%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20expressing%20concern%20over%20the%20venue%20of%20the%20junior%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contests%2C%20she%20said%2C%20were%20being%20held%20in%20a%20stronghold%20of%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh.%20%26quot%3BNow%20imagine%20what%20kind%20of%20atmosphere%20the%20junior%20women%20wrestlers%20will%20be%20competing%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20why%20Nandini%20Nagar%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Gonda%20was%20chosen%20as%20the%20venue%2C%20the%20BJP%20MP%20said%20all%20state%20wrestling%20federations%20had%20backed%20out%20from%20hosting%20the%20contests%20at%20such%20short%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20junior%20nationals%2C%20he%20said%2C%20needed%20to%20be%20held%20at%20the%20earliest%20to%20ensure%20that%20young%20wrestlers%20do%20not%20lose%20a%20year.%20Wrestling%20activities%20have%20remained%20suspended%20since%20the%20wrestlers'%20mega%20protest%20earlier%20this%20year.%20The%20WFI's%20elections%20were%20delayed%20due%20to%20pending%20court%20cases.%20This%20led%20to%20its%20suspension%20by%20the%20international%20wrestling%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20federations%20took%20this%20decision%20together%20for%20the%20resumption%20of%20wrestling%20activities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20MP%20said%20he%20was%20occupied%20with%20preparations%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20due%20next%20year.%20Asked%20why%20he%20met%20BJP%20president%20JP%20Nadda%2C%20he%20said%20Mr%20Nadda%20is%20his%20leader%20and%20that%20there%20was%20no%20discussion%20of%20anything%20related%20to%20WFI%20during%20their%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703416680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F3itgnj1g_brij-bhushan-ani-new_625x300_24_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsanjay-singh-brij-bhushan-sharan-singh-wfi-elections-bjp-mps-bhumihar-rajput-reply-to-question-on-new-wrestling-boss-4734014%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20huge%20row%20surrounding%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20today%20said%20he%20will%20never%20contest%20the%20wrestling%20body's%20polls%20again%20and%20distanced%20himself%20from%20new%20WFI%20president%20Sanjay%20Singh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsanjay-singh-brij-bhushan-shar