states%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20conduct%20such%20a%20survey%20if%20it%20is%20voted%20to%20power%20in%20the%20general%20election%20in%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwhy-the-bjp-is-afraid-of-a-caste-census%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20BJP%20Is%20Afraid%20of%20a%20Caste%20Census%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20earlier%20pressed%20for%20the%20need%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20saying%20that%20it%20reveals%20the%20composition%20of%20OBC%2C%20Dalit%20and%20Adivasi%20communities%20in%20the%20country%20which%20will%20will%20open%20up%20a%20window%20for%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fcongress-state-governments-caste-and-socio-economic-surveys-cwc%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cnew%20development%20paradigm%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20government%20was%20attempting%20to%20turn%20India%20into%20a%20nation%20with%20%E2%80%9Cone%20ideology%2C%20one%20religion%20and%20one%20language.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20they%20kill%20the%20negotiation%2C%20they%20try%20to%20capture%20the%20institutions.%20So%20that%E2%80%99s%20really%20the%20political%20fight%20in%20India%20right%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20feel%20if%20you%20end%20the%20negotiation%20in%20India%2C%20the%20conversation%20between%20the%20union%20India%20collapses%2C%20India%20tears%20itself%20apart.So%20you%20can%20see%20that%20Manipur%20is%20burning%2C%20you%20can%20see%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20burning.%20You%20can%20see%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20a%20problem.%20As%20somebody%20said%20to%20me%20the%20other%20day%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20problem%20on%20the%20edges.%20And%20if%20you%20want%20to%20understand%20a%20system%20you%20got%20to%20look%20at%20the%20edges%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfull%20scale%20civil%20war%E2%80%9D%20is%20underway%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20economic%20inequality%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20economic%20development%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmassively%20concentrating%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20talk%20about%20economic%20development%20you%20have%20to%20ask%20the%20question%20in%20whose%20interest%20is%20that%20economic%20development.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRight%20next%20to%20the%20figure%20of%20growth%20in%20India%2C%20you%20have%20the%20figure%20of%20unemployment%20in%20India.%20So%20India%E2%80%99s%20growing%2C%20but%20the%20way%20it%E2%80%99s%20growing%20is%20by%20massively%20concentrating%20wealth%20towards%20very%20few%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EEconomic%20growth%20without%20meaningful%20employment%20fosters%20inequality%20and%20undermines%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20only%20a%20few%20close%20wealthy%20friends%20of%20the%20government%20are%20benefiting%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20economic%20growth%2C%20leaving%20common%20Indians%20grappling%20with%20unemployment%20and%20price%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FEyHC1SpmwI%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FEyHC1SpmwI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20(%40RahulGandhi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRahulGandhi%2Fstatus%2F1738833537082802422%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2024%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSimilar%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20we%20are%20operating%20on%20a%20debt%20sort%20of%20model%20and%20we%20are%20no%20longer%20producing.%20The%20real%20challenge%20in%20India%20is%20how%20do%20we%20set%20up%20a%20production%20economy%20that%20is%20able%20to%20give%20large%20numbers%20of%20people%20jobs.%20We%20have%20two%20or%20three%20businesses%20that%20are%20pretty%20much%20entire%20business%20system.%20We%20have%20Mr%20%5BGautam%5D%20Adani%2C%20everybody%20knows%20he%20is%20directly%20connected%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20he%20owns%20all%20our%20ports%2C%20airports%2C%20our%20infrastructure.%20With%20that%20kind%20of%20concentration%2C%20you%20will%20get%20growth%20but%20you%20will%20not%20get%20any%20distribution.%20And%20a%20country%20like%20India%20needs%20distribution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20why%20these%20inequalities%20are%20not%20reflecting%20in%20electoral%20outcomes%2C%20Gandhi%20said%20there%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmassive%20mobilisation%E2%80%9D%20but%20there%20is%20a%20requirement%20for%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinfrastructure%20to%20fight%20an%20election%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20a%20fair%20media%2C%20fair%20legal%20system%2C%20fair%20election%20commission%2C%20access%20to%20finance%2C%20institutions%20that%20are%20neutral.%20Imagine%20a%20United%20States%20where%20the%20IRS%2C%20the%20FBI%2C%20their%20full%20time%20job%20is%20destroying%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20opposition.%20So%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20paradigm%20we%E2%80%99re%20in.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20walk%204%2C000%20kilometres%20because%20I%20like%20walking%204%2C000%20kilometres.%20I%20walked%204%2C000%20kilometres%20because%20there%20was%20no%20other%20way%20to%20get%20our%20message%20across.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20my%20social%20media%20is%20fully%20capped.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20got%20a%20shadow%20ban%2024%2F7.%20My%20Twitter%E2%80%99s%20under%20control%2C%20my%20YouTube%20is%20under%20control%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20alone%2C%20the%20entire%20opposition.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20India%20is%20running%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20democracy%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703416344000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01122618%2FF8oQIiNXkAA_m-k.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-trying-to-change-caste-apartheid-system-in-india-not-a-free-democracy-anymore%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%20also%20said%20that%20economic%20development%20is%20%26quot%3Bmassively%20concentrating%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20few.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-trying-to-change-caste-apartheid-system-in-india-not-a-free-democracy-anymore%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bournvita%20Reduces%20Added%20Sugar%20By%2014.4%25%2C%20Influencer%20Calls%20It%20''Big%20Win''%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEight%20months%20after%20an%20influencer%20pointed%20out%20the%20high%20sugar%20content%20in%20Cadbury's%20Bournvita%20chocolate%20'health'%20drink%2C%C2%A0the%20company%20has%20now%20reduced%20the%20quantity%20of%20added%20sugar%20by%2014.4%20percent.%20Previously%2C%20Bournvita%20contained%2037.4%20grams%20of%20added%20sugar%20per%20100%20grams%20of%20powder.%20However%2C%20the%20new%20packaging%20reveals%20that%20it%20has%20a%20reduced%20sugar%20content%20of%2032.2%20grams%20per%20100%20grams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20comes%20after%20Revant%20Himatsingka%20aka%20Food%20Pharmer%2C%20a%20Health%20Influencer%20and%20social%20media%20activist%20highlighted%20the%20drink's%20high%20sugar%20content%2C%20sparking%20widespread%20criticism.%20After%20the%20company's%20big%20move%2C%20Mr%C2%A0Himatsingka%20shared%20the%20development%20in%20an%20Instagram%20reel%20on%20Saturday%20and%20called%20it%20a%20''Big%20Win.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''BIG%20WIN!%20Probably%20the%20first%20time%20in%20history%20that%20an%20INSTAGRAM%20REEL%20led%20to%20a%20food%20giant%20reducing%20its%20sugar%20content!%201%20video%20resulted%20in%20a%2015%25%20reduction%20in%20sugar.%20Imagine%20if%20all%20Indians%20started%20reading%20food%20labels.%20Companies%20wouldn't%20dare%20falsely%20market%20themselves%2C''%20he%20wrote%20while%20sharing%20the%20video.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''This%20fight%20isn't%20against%20Bournvita.%20The%20fight%20is%20against%20any%20company%20that%20sells%20junk%20food%20but%20markets%20itself%20as%20healthy!%20The%20fight%20is%20to%20get%20140%20crore%20Indians%20eating%20healthier!%201%20company%20changing%20its%20sugar%20content%2C%20will%20result%20in%20a%20chain%20reaction%2C%20and%20every%20company%20will%20be%20slightly%20more%20careful%20now%2C''%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20video%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC1MS_Uhriv0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC1MS_Uhriv0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC1MS_Uhriv0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdi