%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01111519%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01111519%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpg%201170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01111519%2Fimage1170x530cropped-300x136.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01111519%2Fimage1170x530cropped-1024x464.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682873%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22530%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20young%20boy%20plays%20in%20the%20street%20amidst%20the%20wreckage%20of%20homes%20destroyed%20by%20airstrikes%20in%20Al%20Shati%20Refugee%20Camp%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20Photo%3A%20UNICEF%2FMohammad%20Ajjour%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20just%20one%20stroke%2C%20a%20few%20hundred%20had%20instantly%20died%2C%20or%20were%20too%20seriously%20injured%20to%20recover.%20He%20found%20to%20his%20horror%20that%20his%20entire%20family%20was%20killed.%20With%20just%20one%20bombing%2C%20he%20was%20orphaned.%20He%20stares%20into%20an%20empty%20future.%20Most%20people%20in%20the%20area%2C%20and%20who%20survived%2C%20were%20not%20thinking%20of%20food%20but%20left%20wondering%20about%20a%20roof%20over%20their%20heads%2C%20burying%20the%20dead%2C%20and%20getting%20on%20with%20their%20lives%2C%20bereaved%20and%20depressed.%20Yet%20at%20the%20end%20of%20that%20strike%2C%20Israeli%20Generals%20were%20gleefully%20totalling%20up%20their%20success%20rates.%20While%20Israel%20finds%20cynical%20delight%20in%20their%20lethal%20battering%2C%20the%20trauma%20never%20ceases%20for%20the%20survivors.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EAl-Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20safe%20place%20to%20shelter%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Palestinian%20health%20ministry%20reports%20that%20as%20deadly%20Israeli%20attacks%20continue%20about%2018%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20and%2049%2C500%20wounded%20in%20Israeli%20attacks%20since%20October%207%2C%20including%C2%A0an%20estimated%20escalation%20of%20close-to%20thousand%20or%20more%20every%20day%20since%20that%20count.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHamas%20militants%20were%20accused%20of%20killing%201%2C400%20Israeli%20civilians%20when%20the%20fighting%20broke%20out%20on%20October%207.%20Truth%20tellers%20have%20revised%20those%20figures%20down%20to%201%2C147%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20contrast%20in%20numbers%20does%20not%20diminish%20the%20losses%20or%20the%20tragic%20consequences%20on%20the%20Israeli%20side%20but%20the%20way%20in%20which%20revenge%20is%20being%20wreaked%20on%20the%20Gazans%20bears%20no%20comparison.%20The%20ignorant%20assume%20that%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20October%207%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0was%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20war.%20Mainstream%20media%2C%20notably%20in%20the%20West%2C%20are%20getting%20the%20public%20to%20make-believe%20that%20October%207%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0was%20the%20original%20day%20in%20the%20Palestine-Israel%20conflict.%20The%20fact%20is%20it%20happened%20in%20the%2075%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20year%20after%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20May%2015%2C%201948%2C%20after%20Israel%20invaded%20Palestine%20and%20grabbed%20land%2C%20dispossessed%20the%20indigenous%20populations%2C%20imposed%20wars%20and%20key%20political%20raids%2C%20and%20kept%20stealing%20land%20after%20each%20occasion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20That%20catastrophe%20that%20beset%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20is%20generally%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20Nakba.%20Whereas%2C%20the%20UN%20Partition%20agreement%20awarded%20the%20Arab%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Estate%20a%20territory%20of%2011%2C100%20square%20kilometres%20or%2042%25%2C%20the%20Jewish%20state%20received%20an%20unjust%20proportion%20%E2%80%93%20a%20territory%20of%2014%2C100%20square%20kilometers%20or%2056%25.%20The%20remaining%202%25%20%E2%80%93%20comprising%20the%20cities%20of%20Jerusalem%2C%20Bethlehem%20and%20the%20adjoining%20area%20%E2%80%93%20were%20to%20become%20an%20international%20zone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20It%20naturally%20led%20to%20wars.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fefraim-halevy-says-israel-guilty-of-seriously-underestimating-hamas%5C%22%3EIsrael%20Guilty%20of%20Seriously%20Underestimating%20Hamas%3B%20War%20Could%20Last%20For%20Years%3A%20Ex-Mossad%20Head%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReclaiming%20land%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20justice%20is%20justified%20even%20under%20international%20law.%20That%20is%20what%20Hamas%20set%20out%20to%20do.%20Today%2C%20Israel%20holds%20over%2078%25%20of%20what%20was%20once%20the%20entirety%20of%20historic%20Palestine.%20Some%20of%20those%20areas%20are%20now%20virtual%20Bantustans%E2%80%99.%20As%20a%20sealed-off%20enclave%2C%20fragmented%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20occupied%20Palestinian%20territory%20(OPT)%20and%20controlled%20by%20Israel%20within%20its%20apartheid%20system%2C%20Gaza%20is%20a%20strip%20of%20land%20that%20can%20in%20many%20respects%20be%20likened%20to%20a%20Bantustan%2C%20when%20the%20indigenous%20people%20were%20shut%20off%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20population.%20The%20Separation%20Wall%20has%20created%20even%20more%20egregious%20apartheid-like%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20it%20is%20a%20fairly%20well%20guarded%20secret%20in%20neo-colonial%20circles%20that%20capturing%20Gaza%20is%20also%20about%20massive%20oil%20resources%20that%20the%20West%20wants%20to%20grab%20for%20its%20use.%20Israel%20plays%20the%20role%20of%20instrument%20in%20return%20for%20armaments%20to%20crush%20the%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20just%20Gaza%20that%20is%20under%20severe%20attack.%20Several%20cities%20and%20villages%20in%20The%20West%20Bank%20are%20also%20under%20constant%20threat%3A%20Jenin%2C%20Sheikh%20Jarrah%2C%20Nablus%2C%20Bethlehem%2C%20and%20several%20towns%20and%20cities%20places%20north%20of%20these%20areas%20with%20nightly%20attacks.%20The%20war%20is%20broadening%20and%20both%20sides%20are%20terrified%20of%20potential%20costs.%20Israel%20fears%20how%20Hamas%20is%20joined%20by%20Hezbollah%20and%20other%20resistance%20groups%2C%20even%20countries%20opposed%20to%20Israel%2C%20in%20the%20region.%20Yemen%20has%20hindered%20ships%20from%20and%20to%20Israel%20from%20using%20waters%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20costing%20Israel%20millions%20more%20to%20transport%20their%20goods.%20The%20need%20for%20a%20just%20and%20lasting%20peace%20is%20urgent%20because%20if%20the%20war%20to%20spread%2C%20it%20could%20only%20harm%20the%20entire%20global%20economy%20and%20global%20security.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29164358%2FF_xf5OOXwAAsXcb.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29164358%2FF_xf5OOXwAAsXcb.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29164358%2FF_xf5OOXwAAsXcb-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29164358%2FF_xf5OOXwAAsXcb-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686953%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDestroyed%20buildings%20in%20Gaza.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40UNRWA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20time%20to%20celebrate%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20what%20should%20Christmas%202023%20resemble%20for%20Christians%20and%20their%20churches%20in%20this%20context%3F%20The%20churches%20in%20Palestine%20are%20setting%20the%20tone.%20Christmas%20celebrations%20in%20Bethlehem%20have%20been%20cancelled.%20The%20Heads%20of%20Churches%20in%20The%20Holy%20Land%20have%20declared%20that%20there%20cannot%20be%20celebrations%20for%20as%20long%20as%20the%20Israeli%20genocide%20of%20Palestinians%20is%20on.%20They%20now%20have%20to%20pick%20Christ%20from%20the%20rubble%20of%20the%20shattered%20homes%2C%20schools%2C%20hospitals%2C%20and%20other%20buildings%20that%20house%20vital%20project%20services.%20The%20Churches%20have%20asked%20that%20people%20stay%20in%20silence%20and%20pray%20for%20the%20victims%20and%20for%20peace.%20This%20should%20be%20a%20mandate%20for%20churches%20all%20over%20the%20world.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChristians%20are%20now%20passing%20through%20the%20season%20of%20Advent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EAdvent%20is%20a%20season%20observed%20in%20most%20Christian%20denominations%20as%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20time%20of%20expectant%20waiting%20and%20preparation%20for%20both%20the%20celebration%20of%20the%20Nativity%20of%20Christ%20at%20Christmas%20and%20the%20return%20of%20Christ%20at%20the%20Second%20Coming%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAdvent%20is%20the%20time%20to%20recall%20how%20god%20embraced%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20of%20people%20%E2%80%93%20the%20vulnerable%2C%20voiceless%2C%20poor%2C%20homeless%2C%20the%20marginalised%2C%20and%20the%20forgotten.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChristmas%202023%20is%20hardly%20the%20time%20to%20be%20celebrating%20when%20people%20in%20the%20entire%20Holy%20Land%20are%20suffering%20severe%20oppression.%20A%20relay%20of%20funerals%20is%20what%20one%20witnesses%20every%20day.%20If%20Christians%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20are%20planning%20celebrations%2C%20they%20must%20be%20conscious%20of%20the%20violence%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.%20Just%20as%20Christ%20draws%20us%20to%20a%20journey%20where%20we%20shift%20from%20material%20celebration%20to%20those%20who%20are%20trampled%20over%20by%20the%20rich%20and%20powerful%2C%20the%20homeless%20and%20uninvited%2C%20the%20bombed%20and%20isolated%2C%20Christians%20are%20called%20to%20work%20for%20%E2%80%98peace%20on%20earth%E2%80%99%2C%20and%2C%20at%20this%20moment%2C%20notably%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChrist%20himself%20was%20born%20into%20the%20world%20unsolicited%20and%20as%20a%20source%20of%20annoyance%20to%20the%20ruling%20classes%20of%20those%20times.%20After%20finding%20no%20room%20to%20give%20birth%20to%20Jesus%2C%20Joseph%20and%20Mary%20who%20had%20traversed%20miles%20and%20miles%20upon%20a%20donkey%20where%20Mary%20could%20give%20birth%20to%20her%20baby%20found%20them%20rejected%20in%20place%20after%20place.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20night%20in%20Bethlehem%20is%20lived%20out%20today%20every%20day.%20This%20is%20the%20world%20at%20its%20worst%20regardless%20of%20where%20you%20are%20%E2%80%93%20Gaza%2C%20West%20Bank%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20Dalits%20and%20Tribals%20of%20India%2C%20Manipur%20in%20India%20and%20to%20the%20people%20in%20the%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98forever%20wars%E2%80%99%20in%20Africa%20as%20in%20Congo%2C%20Cameroon%2C%20Ethiopia%2C%20Mozambique%2C%20Mali%2C%20Burkina%20Faso%2C%20South%20Sudan%2C%20and%20in%20Asia%20%E2%80%93%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20and%20West%20Papua.%20There%20is%20a%20colonial%20agenda%20behind%20each%20of%20these%20wars%20and%20they%20are%20about%20natural%20resources.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123715%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123715%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpeg%201170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123715%2Fimage1170x530cropped-300x136.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123715%2Fimage1170x530cropped-1024x464.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688063%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22530%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPeople%20search%20for%20their%20belongings%20in%20the%20rubble%20in%20the%20Nuseirat%20refugee%20camp%20in%20Gaza.%20Photo%3A%20UNRWA%2FAshraf%20Amra%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20the%20rubric%20of%20the%20expression%20%E2%80%98festive%20season%E2%80%99%2C%20commerce%20multiplies.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ECorporate%20interests%20play%20up%20Christmas%20because%20it%20attracts%20consumer%20interests%2C%20which%20are%20a%20kind%20of%20opium%20that%20prevents%20working%20for%20real%20peace%20based%20on%20justice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20world%20observes%20Christmas%20in%202023%2C%20the%20church%20must%20preach%20hope%20and%20justice%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20hate%2C%20and%20war.%20It%20must%20rebuff%20those%20who%20practice%20caste%2C%20class%2C%20ethnic%20superiority%20and%2C%20in%20its%20place%2C%20summon%20people%20to%20practice%20equity.%20In%20the%20midst%20of%20genocide%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20in%20Gaza%2C%20but%20wherever%20else%20there%20is%20oppression%20and%20cruelty%2C%20the%20church%20must%20practice%20the%20true%20meaning%20of%20Christmas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20true%20meaning%20of%20Christmas%20is%20found%20in%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FThe_American_Magazine%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20American%20Magazine%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(1889).%20I%20quote%3A%20Christmas%20calls%20on%20Christians%20%E2%80%9Cto%20give%20up%20one%E2%80%99s%20very%20self%20%E2%80%93%20to%20think%20only%20of%20others%20%E2%80%93%20how%20to%20bring%20the%20greatest%20happiness%20to%20others.%E2%80%9D%20That%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20demands%20sacrifice.%20For%20Christ%E2%80%99s%20journey%20itself%20was%20a%20journey%20from%20%E2%80%98The%20manger%20to%20the%20Cross%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20thorny%20path%20in%20which%20he%20confronted%20the%20rich%2C%20powerful%2C%20and%20cruel.%20To%20claim%20Christmas%20as%20a%20festival%20of%20peace%2C%20love%2C%20and%20hope%2C%20is%20to%20engage%20in%20costly%20solidarity%20with%20the%20weak%20and%20powerless.%20Or%20else%2C%20we%20will%20be%20emptying%20Christmas%20from%20its%20very%20essence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMay%20this%20Christmas%20season%20be%20a%20time%20when%20humankind%2C%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20can%20aspire%20to%20a%20just%20world%20where%20death%20and%20destruction%20are%20left%20behind%20and%20an%20authentic%20peace%20be%20positioned%20through%20constant%20dialogue.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ERanjan%20Solomon%20is%20a%20political%20commentator%2Fhuman%20rights%20activist%2C%20and%20a%20long-time%20Palestine%20solidarity%20advocate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703414769000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24161457%2FScreenshot-2023-12-24-at-4.09.24.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fpalestine-genocide-christmas-israel%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Christmas%202023%20is%20hardly%20the%20time%20to%20be%20celebrating%20when%20people%20in%20the%20entire%20Holy%20Land%20are%20suffering%20severe%20oppression.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2