er%20men%20out%20there%26quot%3B.%20The%20minister%20met%20his%20wife%20at%20university%20and%20they%20have%20two%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20discussions%20at%20Downing%20Street%20receptions%20are%20regarded%20as%20%26quot%3Boff%20the%20record%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20subject%20to%20media%20coverage.%20However%2C%20the%20Sunday%20Mirror%20stated%20that%20it%20had%20chosen%20to%20defy%20this%20tradition%20due%20to%20Mr%20Cleverly's%20standing%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20his%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Mr%20Cleverly%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20what%20was%20always%20understood%20as%20a%20private%20conversation%2C%20James%2C%20the%20home%20secretary%2C%20tackling%20spiking%20made%20what%20was%20clearly%20meant%20to%20be%20an%20ironic%20joke%20-%20for%20which%20he%20apologises.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20politicians%20from%20the%20Labour%20Party%20criticised%20Mr%20Cleverly's%20statement.%20The%20Shadow%20Minister%20for%20Domestic%20Violence%20and%20Safeguarding%2C%20Alex%20Davies-Jones%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B'It%20was%20a%20joke'%20is%20the%20most%20tired%20excuse%20in%20the%20book%20and%20no%20one%20is%20buying%20it.%20If%20the%20home%20secretary%20is%20serious%20about%20tackling%20spiking%2C%20and%20violence%20against%20women%20and%20girls%2C%20then%20that%20requires%20a%20full%20cultural%20change.%20The%20'banter'%20needs%20to%20stop%20and%20it%20has%20to%20start%20at%20the%20top.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpiking%20is%20a%20disturbing%20and%20serious%20crime%20which%20is%20having%20a%20devastating%20impact%20on%20young%20women's%20lives.%20It%20is%20truly%20unbelievable%20that%20the%20home%20secretary%20made%20such%20appalling%20jokes%20on%20the%20very%20same%20day%20the%20government%20announced%20new%20policy%20on%20spiking%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shadow%20Home%20Secretary%20Yvette%20Cooper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20Ms%20Cleverly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https