sh-to-get-passports-to-leave-zimbabwe-is-fed-by-economic-gloom-and-a-price-hike%2Famp_articleshow%2F106248843.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blockades%20Test%20Manipur's%20Move%20To%20Open%20Highways%2C%20Bring%20Normalcy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20government's%20decision%20to%20open%20two%20key%20highways%20in%20the%20state%20is%20facing%20resistance%20in%20the%20hill%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20to%20fully%20secure%20the%20highways%20during%20the%20Christmas%20season%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20big%20step%20towards%20restoring%20peace%20in%20the%20state%20where%20over%20180%20people%20have%20died%20and%20thousands%20have%20been%20internally%20displaced%20since%20violence%20began%20on%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shutdown%20called%20by%20the%20Kuki%20groups%2C%20however%2C%20puts%20the%20first%20small%20steps%20to%20peace%20at%20risk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20posted%20extra%20security%20forces%20on%20the%20two%20highways%20to%20resume%20bus%20services%20from%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%20to%20Mao%20to%20the%20north%2C%20passing%20via%20Kangpokpi%2C%20and%20from%20Imphal%20to%20Churachandpur%20to%20the%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20two%20routes%20pass%20through%20hill%20and%20valley%20areas%20that%20have%20seen%20violence%20between%20the%20hill-majority%20Kuki%20tribes%20and%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20buses%20that%20left%20for%20Mao%2C%20110%20km%20from%20Imphal%2C%20returned%20midway%20after%20facing%20a%20large%20number%20of%20protesters%20who%20blocked%20the%20road%20in%20Kangpokpi%2C%20despite%20the%20presence%20of%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20show%20people%20armed%20with%20single-barrel%20guns%20among%20the%20crowds%20stopping%20vehicles%20before%20allowing%20them%20to%20proceed%20after%20checking%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22