prevent%20any%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Churachandpur%2C%20the%20ITLF%20has%20said%20all%20non-tribals%20within%20the%20district%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20move%20out%20and%20non-tribal%20from%20outside%20are%20can't%20move%20inside%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestions%20have%20been%20raised%20over%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20civil%20society%20groups%20whose%20aggressive%20actions%20appear%20to%20be%20only%20fuelling%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20NDTV%20on%20Saturday%20it%20was%20expected%20that%20in%20the%20initial%20days%2C%20many%20people%20would%20not%20turn%20up%2C%20especially%20after%20Kuki%20civil%20society%20groups%20opposed%20the%20move%20to%20open%20the%20highways.%20What%20is%20inexplicable%20is%20the%20shutdown%20of%20the%20districts%20by%20pressure%20groups%20when%20the%20authorities%20have%20ensured%20safe%20commute%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20adding%20they%20have%20come%20across%20hundreds%20of%20people%20who%20fled%20their%20burning%20homes%20and%20want%20to%20return%20to%20rebuild%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20groups'%20move%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20districts%20stem%20from%20their%20allegations%20that%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20functioned%20with%20bias%20in%20how%20they%20operated%20amid%20the%20violence.%20The%20Manipur%20government's%20attempt%20to%20send%20police%20personnel%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20where%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20are%20settled%20had%20also%20faced%20strong%20resistance%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20border%20town%20Moreh%20near%20Myanmar%2C%20Churachandpur%2C%20and%20Kangpokpi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20November%2029%20specifically%20pointed%20out%20the%20role%20of%20some%20civil%20society%20groups%20in%20keeping%20tensions%20in%20Manipur%20simmering%2C%20during%20a%20hearing%20on%20burying%20bodies%20kept%20in%20morgues.%20Ordering%20the%20petitioners%20to%20bury%20the%20dead%20respectfully%20in%20designated%20sites%20instead%20of%20govern