20who%20have%20studied%20only%20Hindi%20with%20those%20who%20know%20English.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20he%20says%20those%20who%20study%20only%20Hindi%20in%20Bihar%20%26quot%3Bbuild%20houses%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bclean%20toilets%26quot%3B%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20because%20they%20(people%20here)%20studied%20English%2C%20today%20they%20earn%20fat%20salaries%20in%20IT%20companies.%20They%20say%20'Hindi%20Hindi'.%20You%20know%20well%20who%20build%20buildings.%20Those%20who%20study%20only%20Hindi%20in%20Bihar%20build%20houses%20for%20us%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20sweep%20roads%20and%20clean%20toilets%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Maran%20was%20heard%20saying%20in%20the%20video%20that%20has%20now%20gone%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI.N.D.I%20Alliance%20leader%20and%20DMK%20MP%20Dayanidhi%20Maran%20says%20Hindi%20speakers%20from%20UP%20and%20Bihar%20come%20and%20clean%20toilets%20in%20TN.%3Cbr%3E%5CnRahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20must%20clarify%2C%20if%20this%20is%20the%20stated%20position%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20JDU%20too.%3Cbr%3E%5CnI.N.D.I%20Alliance's%20divisive%20agenda%20is%20out%20in%20full%20force%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fi4wwLbYisW%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fi4wwLbYisW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Amit%20Malviya%20(%40amitmalviya)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Famitmalviya%2Fstatus%2F1738828917555757521%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2024%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mr%20Maran%20could%20not%20be%20reached%2C%20sources%20from%20the%20DMK%20have%20claimed%20it%20was%20an%20old%20video%20that%20has%20been%20recirculated%20by%20the%20BJP.%20The%20DMK%20sources%20said%20the%20BJP%20has%20recirculated%20the%20video%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20the%20backlash%C2%A0Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20faces%20amid%20her%20fa