bout%20finishing%20Sanatan%2C%20now%20they%20are%20targeting%20labourers.%20This%20is%20unfortunate.%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20derives%20enjoyment%20from%20such%20remarks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leader%20Amit%20Malviya%20shared%20the%20video%2C%20saying%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20should%20clarify%20if%20the%20DMK%20leader's%20remarks%20are%20in%20line%20with%20their%20parties'%20position.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20INDIA%20parties%20influential%20in%20the%20northern%20part%20of%20the%20country%20were%20caught%20on%20a%20sticky%20wicket%20by%20Mr%20Stalin's%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20remarks.%20The%20fresh%20controversy%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20is%20racing%20against%20time%20to%20iron%20out%20internal%20conflicts%20and%20regional%20rivalries%20and%20gear%20up%20for%20the%20big%20fight%20against%20a%20formidable%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703409600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F4k48p1mo_tejashwi-yadav-dayanidhi-maran_625x300_24_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdayanidhi-maran-giriraj-singh-tejashwi-yadav-dmk-mps-bihar-people-clean-toilets-video-may-be-india-blocs-new-trouble-4733186%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20video%20of%20DMK%20leader%20Dayanidhi%20Maran%2C%20which%20party%20sources%20claim%20is%20old%2C%20can%20spell%20trouble%20for%20the%20unity%20of%20INDIA%20bloc%20at%20a%20time%20when%20it%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20big%20Lok%20Sabha%20contest%20just%20a%20few%20months%20away.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdayanidhi-maran-giriraj-singh-tejashwi-yadav-dmk-mps-bihar-people-clean-toilets-video-may-be-india-blocs-new-trouble-4733186%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdayanidhi-maran-giriraj-singh