9s%20turf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20sports%20ministry%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fsport-others%2Fgovt-suspends-wrestling-federation-new-body-complete-control-former-office-bearers-9080900%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EIndian%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20notes%20that%20Sanjay%20Singh%20has%20shown%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98blatant%20disregard%20for%20the%20established%20legal%20and%20procedural%20norms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOlympics%20bronze%20medalist%20Sakshi%20Malik%20had%2C%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20election%2C%20announced%20that%20she%20is%20giving%20up%20the%20sport%20in%20protest.%C2%A0%20Olympian%20Bajrang%20Punia%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGoongaPahalwan%2Fstatus%2F1738229846533402663%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1738229846533402663%257Ctwgr%255E75a1598bbc969d22787a9ff71edeb9e1307af55d%257Ctwcon%255Es1_c10%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ndtv.com%252Findia-news%252Fsakshi-malik-row-i-will-also-return-padma-shri-says-wrestler-virender-singh-in-battle-against-brij-bhushan-4727707%5C%22%3EDeaflympics%20gold%20medallist%20Virender%20Singh%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20returned%20and%20announced%20the%20return%20of%20their%20medals%20and%20Padma%20Shri%20awards%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20evening%2C%20Malik%20had%20posed%20on%20concerns%20voiced%20by%20junior%20wrestlers%20over%20the%20choice%20of%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGonda%20is%20the%20area%20of%20%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8BBrijbhushan.%20Now%20imagine%20in%20what%20environment%20the%20junior%20women%20wrestlers%20will%20go%20there%20to%20wrestle.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIs%20there%20no%20place%20in%20this%20country%20to%20hold%20nationals%20other%20than%20Nandini%20Nagar%3F%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20wrote%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sports%20ministry%20said%20the%20Gonda%20announcement%20did%20not%20gi