height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EHundreds%20of%20people%20participated%20in%20the%20funeral%20prayers%20of%20the%20slain%20retired%20police%20officer%20whose%20security%20detail%20was%20recently%20withdrawn%20by%20the%20local%20administration.%20(Photo%3A%20Sajad%20Hameed)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShot%20while%20issuing%20call%20to%20prayer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20his%20brother%2C%20Abdul%20Karim%20Mir%2C%20said%20that%20like%20on%20any%20other%20day%2C%20Shafi%20had%20left%20home%20before%20dawn%20to%20issue%20the%20prayer%20call%20from%20the%20neighbourhood%20mosque.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20when%20he%20was%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20%3Cem%3Eazaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(call%20for%20prayer)%2C%20we%20heard%20a%20shot%20and%20the%20azaan%20was%20cut%20shot%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20took%20much%20notice%2C%E2%80%9D%20Karim%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20live%20in%20a%20peaceful%20area.%20Even%20when%20militancy%20was%20at%20its%20peak%2C%20we%20were%20leading%20normal%20lives.%20After%20some%2010-15%20minutes%2C%20my%20daughter-in-law%20heard%20the%20sound%20of%20wailing%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarim%20said%20that%20by%20the%20time%20he%20reached%20the%20mosque%2C%20his%20brother%20had%20been%20taken%20to%20hospital%20by%20locals%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20blood%20in%20the%20mosque.%20I%20thought%20he%20had%20collapsed%20and%20suffered%20a%20brain%20haemorrhage%20because%20of%20which%20blood%20smeared%20the%20floor.%20But%20when%20I%20reached%20the%20hospital%2C%20I%20learnt%20that%20he%20was%20shot%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20news%20of%20the%20shootout%20spread%2C%20Shafi%E2%80%99s%20native%20village%20is%20learned%20to%20have%20plunged%20into%20shock%20and%20grief.%20Additional%20security%20personnel%20were%20rushed%20to%20the%20area%20and%20carried%20out%20searches%20to%20track%20down%20the%20attackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20villagers%20attended%20the%20funeral%20prayers%20of%20Shafi%2C%20who%20is%20survived%20by%20his%20wife%20and%20two%20children%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20is%20a%20teacher.%20Amid%20emotional%20scenes%2C%20the%20slain%20police%20officer%20was%20laid%20to%20rest%20at%20his%20ancestral%20graveyard%20in%20Gantmulla%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20an%20officer%20among%20officers%20and%20a%20farmer%20among%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ghulam%20Rasool%20Mir%2C%20a%20retired%20sub-inspector%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20while%20participating%20in%20the%20funeral%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20first%20such%20incident%20in%20our%20village.%20And%20it%20has%20brought%20more%20uncertainty%20into%20the%20lives%20of%20retired%20police%20officers%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETargeted%20killings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20attack%20in%20north%20Kashmir%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20a%20spate%20of%20targeted%20killings%20in%20which%20members%20of%20the%20minority%20Pandit%20community%20and%20migrant%20workers%20were%20shot%20dead%20by%20militants%20in%202021%20across%20the%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20retired%20SSP%E2%80%99s%20killing%20comes%20days%20after%20a%20police%20constable%20was%20shot%20and%20injured%20in%20a%20targeted%20attack%20at%20Hamdaniya%20Colony%20in%20Bemina%20area%20of%20Srinagar%20and%20less%20than%20two%20months%20after%20an%20off-duty%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20head%20constable%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20similar%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Masroor%20Ahmad%20Wani%2C%20a%20police%20inspector%2C%20was%20shot%20while%20he%20was%20playing%20cricket%20at%20a%20ground%20near%20his%20home%20in%20Eidgah%20locality%20of%20Srinagar.%20After%20battling%20for%20life%20for%20several%20days%2C%20the%20victim%20was%20later%20shifted%20to%20AIIMS%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20where%20he%20succumbed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20witnessed%20a%20surge%20in%20militant%20attacks%20with%20the%20casualties%20suffered%20by%20security%20forces%20this%20year%20surpassing%20the%202022%20figure%2C%20official%20data%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20Army%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20and%20two%20others%20were%20injured%20when%20militants%20ambushed%20two%20Army%20vehicles%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20site%20of%20an%20anti-militancy%20operation%20in%20Poonch%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20territory%20is%20reeling%20under%20tensions%20after%20the%20families%20of%20the%20three%20civilians%2C%20who%20were%20picked%20by%20the%20army%20for%20questioning%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20attack%2C%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20tortured%20and%20killed%20in%20custody%2C%20prompting%20the%20administration%20to%20order%20a%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703395480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24151923%2FIMG_2992-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fkashmir-top-cop-mohammad-shafi-mir-shot-dead%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohammad%20Shafi%20Mir%2C%20who%20had%20devoted%20himself%20to%20social%20service%20after%20retirement%2C%20was%20a%20muezzin%20at%20a%20local%20mosque%20in%20his%20village%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A55%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fkashmir-top-cop-mohammad-shafi-mir-shot-dead%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20gives%20birth%20to%20two%20babies%20in%20two%20days%3A%20Know%20more%20about%20this%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703395478000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106245103%2Cimgsize-1062480.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Fparenting%2Fmoments%2Fwoman-gives-birth-to-tw