ion%20at%20Rashtriya%20Raksha%20University%2C%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20India%20has%20formally%20lodged%20a%20protest%20with%20the%20United%20States%20and%20reiterated%20that%20extremists%20and%20separatist%20forces%20targeting%20India%20should%20not%20get%20space%20outside%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20seen%20the%20news.%20As%20you%20know%2C%20we%20are%20concerned%20about%20this.%20Extremists%20and%20separatist%20forces%20outside%20India%20should%20not%20get%20space.%20Our%20consulate%20has%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20%5BUS%5D%20government%20and%20the%20police%20there%20over%20whatever%20happened%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20the%20matter%20is%20being%20inquired%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20PTI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20consulate%20in%20San%20Francisco%20denounced%20the%20alleged%20vandalism%20of%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWe%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20defacing%20of%20SMVS%20Shri%20Swaminarayan%20Mandir%20at%20Newark%2C%20California%20with%20anti-India%20graffiti.%20This%20incident%20has%20hurt%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20Indian%20community.%20We%20have%20pressed%20for%20quick%20investigation%20and%20prompt%20action%20against%20the%20vandals%20by%20the%20US%20authorities%20in%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20India%20in%20SF%20(%40CGISFO)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCGISFO%2Fstatus%2F1738390168615489922%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20PTI%2C%20the%20Newark%20police%20said%20any%20acts%20or%20threats%20of%20violence%2C%20property%20damage%2C%20harassment%2C%20intimidation%20or%20other%20crimes%20motivated%20by%20hate%20or%20bias%20are%20considered%20very%20serious%20and%20