20interest%20in%20starting%20his%20own%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20for%20EleFant%20emerged%20from%20the%20desire%20to%20provide%20the%20best%20toys%20for%20my%20daughter%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20brand%20for%20parents%20like%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20business%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20in%2014%20cities%20so%20far.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334717%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20business%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20in%2014%20cities%20so%20far.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20The%20EleFant%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20changing%20family%20dynamics%2C%20Sourabh%20observed%20the%20increasing%20challenge%20for%20parents%20who%20juggle%20work%20and%20home%20responsibilities%20simultaneously.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20time%2C%20I%20would%20be%20working%2C%20leaving%20little%20room%20to%20go%20out%20and%20search%20for%20toys.%20I%20wanted%20to%20simplify%20one%20thing%20for%20working%20parents%20like%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transition%20from%20the%20